21:11.002 --> 21:13.570
Hey, I can't believe this,

21:13.604 --> 21:16.106
But somebody destroyed my room.

21:17.975 --> 21:19.576
What are you talking about?

21:19.610 --> 21:21.244
Everything I own.

21:21.279 --> 21:23.780
- Completely ruined.
- What?

21:27.318 --> 21:30.153
Well, now that my
room is destroyed,

21:30.188 --> 21:34.257
Mom and dad will never believe
I destroyed your room, too.

21:34.292 --> 21:36.259
Guess I showed you, alex.

21:38.196 --> 21:42.632
Max, you are lobbing this one
so high up for her right now.

21:42.667 --> 21:46.570
Oh yeah? Take a look at
this whole box of lob.

21:47.972 --> 21:50.540
- Your clock radio is broken?
- Yep.

21:50.575 --> 21:53.009
- Your lava lamp is lava-less?
- Mm-hm.

21:53.044 --> 21:56.379
And your ceramic hamburger
has a gnarly bite out of it?

21:56.414 --> 21:58.181
You got that right.

21:59.684 --> 22:03.119
Wow, max. You sure got me by
wrecking all of your own stuff.

22:03.154 --> 22:05.589
That's right I got you. Wait...

22:07.625 --> 22:09.926
Oh, man. I think I got me.

22:11.629 --> 22:13.396
Dude, this is mine.

22:13.431 --> 22:14.598
So you got her too.

22:14.732 --> 22:17.267
Sucker. High five, brother.

